Class AdministratorView

Object
AdministratorView
All Implemented Interfaces:
ViewInterface
public class AdministratorView extends Object implements ViewInterface
The AdministratorView class provides the user interface for the administrator to interact with the hospital management system. It allows administrators to manage hospital staff, view appointments, manage medication inventory, and approve replenishment requests. Implements the `ViewInterface`.
